target: style_guide
validations:
  - name: palette_exports
    type: agent_validation
    severity: error
    args:
      rubric: >
        Verify that the style guide module exports a comprehensive color palette object
        or set of named color constants covering at least: grass/ground colors, water colors,
        path colors, UI background colors (HUD, sidebar), button colors, and status bar colors
        (health, happiness). The palette should be importable by other modules.

  - name: font_constants
    type: agent_validation
    severity: error
    args:
      rubric: >
        Verify that the style guide module exports font configuration constants including
        at least: a minimum font size (12px or larger), HUD text size (16px or larger),
        and menu/title text size (32px or larger). These should be exported as named
        constants or as part of a FONTS configuration object.

  - name: tile_size_constant
    type: agent_validation
    severity: error
    args:
      rubric: >
        Verify that a TILE_SIZE constant (value 32) is exported from either the style guide
        module or constants.js, and is available for import by other modules. This constant
        should be used for all tile-to-pixel and pixel-to-tile conversions.
